Date: Sun, 4 Jan 2026 11:54:51 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 15/50] Remove unused S3 management code

Summary:
This code was introduced in https://github.com/phacility/libphutil/commit/d6744fb7156134a5b46f818b3bd72c94fdebc1af along with a `bin/aws-s3` command to use it.

When libphutil was scrappeed, the entire `src/future` directory was copied unchanged into Arcanist, however the `scripts/` and `bin/` directories were not.

Hence this code is unreachable. Remove it as dead.

Test Plan: Read the code, grep the Phorge and Arcanist repos for usage of this code and find none

Reviewers: O1 Blessed Committers, aklapper

Reviewed By: O1 Blessed Committers, aklapper

Subscribers: aklapper, tobiaswiese, valerio.bozzolan, Matthew, Cigaryno

Differential Revision: https://we.phorge.it/D26615
